Package org.openlca.simapro.csv.model

Class Uncertainty

java.lang.Object
org.openlca.simapro.csv.model.Uncertainty
public class Uncertainty extends Object
Stores the parameters of an uncertainty distribution. In SimaPro, depending on the distribution function, 3 parameters can be used to store this information:

parameter 1:
  • Normal: doubled standard deviation
  • Lognormal: squared geometric standard deviation
  • Triangle: empty
  • Uniform: empty

parameter 2:
  • Normal: empty
  • Lognormal: empty
  • Triangle: minimum
  • Uniform: minimum
parameter 3:
  • Normal: empty
  • Lognormal: empty
  • Triangle: maximum
  • Uniform: maximum
